{"tid":1667252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新屋嶺既手足","createTime":"2019-10-21T10:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:18.000Z","uid":264669,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a0061c29a3dbf4840b3b125bd0d2aa70ee9de5e","tid":1667252,"uid":264669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"我想問點解依家無哂新屋嶺既消息既？D手足俾人放哂出去？定係已經被處理好哂？定係我地已經唔記得左佢地啦😭"},{"pid":"c9ba3f115f046f30a87010406ea8d3f8bf59c761","tid":1667252,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:58:19.000Z","msg":"個個掛住查案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a517a0418a712a80bb776bc016e344d3b73ed7","tid":1667252,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"56a397083b9d2af843902e02226c2ff90752d520","tid":1667252,"uid":177438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:59:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"24a980a335a6eeee734e484bde77cb9c8e9e6d4a","tid":1667252,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"a415805862004ce330dd2463c608673bb7daa1ad","tid":1667252,"uid":264669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:09:14.000Z","msg":"見唔到有post講佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5404298e932ee988761bbce26af3e258e6588c5d","tid":1667252,"uid":109032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:21:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"216bb785c970977bb84b80c72cf40da4f11a35df","tid":1667252,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}